                                    <p xmlns="">Mobil Delvac 1 ESP 0W-40 is recommended for use in 4-stroke diesel engines, including modern low emission engines with Exhaust Gas Recirculation (EGR), After Treatment systems with Diesel Particulate Filters (DPF&rsquo;s) and Diesel Oxidation Catalysts (DOC&rsquo;s). These applications include the following:</p>
